What's that?  Did you mean Austere?  
<br />

<br />
From memory, the items that lower Carbuncle cost are:
<br />
Avatar Belt -   Cost -2 (but for SMN as sub only... doesn't count)
<br />
Conjurer's Ring -  Cost -2 (yellow hp latent effect)
<br />
Austere Robe -   Cost -1
<br />
Carbuncle Mitts - Cost -2
<br />
Light Staff - Cost -6
<br />
Apollo Staff - Cost - 8?  &lt;--- Not sure of the exact amount
<br />
Vermillion Cloak - MP+1 (So, Cost-1)
<br />

<br />
Now, keep in mind that at higher levels, it costs more to keep Carbuncle out.  But, if you got the right setup to regen mp while Carbuncle is out.  
<br />

<br />
Tthe Robe, Ring, Apollo Staff and Cloak are all buyable.  But, I don't think you'll be regening MP without those Mitts if you were level 70+.  SMN become godlike when they have all this gear.  Any monkey can farm enough gil for those other items, but you will need the help of some good friends to make your SMN incredibly powerful.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
