				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Keeping your SMN skill up pays off in the end.  A higher summoning skill increases the survivability of your avatar.  Later on, SMN can kill some high level NMs solo with Carbuncle.  However, Carbuncle won't stand a chance (and neither will you) with a low summoning skill.
<br />

<br />
I just saw that SMN beat Maat for the level 70 cap last night... I think all that summoning skill paid off for that battle.  Titan was able to last against Maat and Ramuh for about a minute and a half (that's pretty good for 2 level 70ish mobs hitting it).</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
