				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I just saw that summoner on Leviathan get Fenrir last night... the Fenrir battle is very tough.  They had PLD, WAR/NIN, THF/NIN, BRD/WHM, WHM/BLM, SMN/WHM (most 75).  I think they wiped three times and beat him the fourth time.  
<br />

<br />
