<br />

<br />
Unlike the other avatar battles (the level 60 ones), those can be solo-ed or duoed by level 75s, so it is possible for a lower level character to get the whispers for Fenrir.  But, I fail to see how they could have defeated Fenrir with a 5 person PT + 1 low level.  
